{"tid":658980,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"神級女友好撚正 我犯吾犯賤?","createTime":"2018-05-09T12:30:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T16:11:23.000Z","uid":185975,"like":1,"dislike":119,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e3e29c248a77babe36566ff9a1e24dd29e7bb303","tid":658980,"uid":185975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T12:30:35.000Z","msg":"講下條女先喇<br />\n吾係靓到女神級  36D 25歲  <br />\n出街行會有人吸下咁 <br />\n自問我普通樣但作為佢條仔好撚威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出街AA  煮飯好食 溫柔<br />\n就晒我 無不良嗜好 乖乖女 <br />\n乾淨 孝順 識做家務<br />\n好撚有母愛 出得廳堂 上得大床<br />\n開頭擔心我父母吾中意佢 點知錫到佢窿<br />\n佢放工就會反屋企 周不時約下FD敘舊咁吾蒲 <br />\n由得我打機又吾會吵9住晒 吾應機都吾嬲9我<br />\n開頭覺得佢好撚正 香港地邊有呢d女<br />\n周街港女就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對於男人來講 吾麻煩又易就既女人真係何求<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<br />\n後悔莫及 已被分手 <br />\n衰在我吾識珍惜佢 自己爛玩 成日吾理佢 吾關心佢<br />\n安全到我諗住過多幾年可以直接娶佢番屋企<br />\n香港地仲有冇第二條女比反我????<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b70cf8d3c990718266d6060126ebc7d888f1ae","tid":658980,"uid":51041,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T12:31:39.000Z","msg":"圖呢？"},{"pid":"dc7e59073c55e932aa87adcf10392b30e039e77a","tid":658980,"uid":30604,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T12:31:39.000Z","msg":"大陸仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b3f24a9a431a38f456abb29952d15d755280136","tid":658980,"uid":138138,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T12:32:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/09/203225_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F09%2F203225